====Noun====
{{en-noun|-}} (''rarely used in the singular'')

# {{context|British|vulgar|lang=en}} The [[testicle]]s (''sometimes used in the singular'')
# {{context|British|vulgar|lang=en}} Nonsense or information deliberately intended to mislead.
#: ''That's a load of '''bollocks''', mate!''
# {{context|Ireland|vulgar|lang=en}} An [[idiot]], an [[ignorant]] or disagreeable person.
#: ''Don't mind him; he's only an oul' '''bollocks'''!''
# {{context|British|vulgar|lang=en}} A contraction of '''[[dog's bollocks|the dog's bollocks]]'''.

